01:07:22.770 --> 01:07:28.170
And it says that, if a particle
has a certain momentum, that is

01:07:28.170 --> 01:07:31.320
has a certain mass
time velocity--

01:07:31.320 --> 01:07:34.920
OK, so if a particle
has a certain momentum,

01:07:34.920 --> 01:07:39.210
it will also display
wave-like properties.

01:07:39.210 --> 01:07:43.770
And the wavelength typical
of those wave-like properties

01:07:43.770 --> 01:07:45.670
